  "about_app_description": "VRS App is a digital field registration system for bird ringers and nest monitors. The app consists of two modules: a ringing module for recording catches and a nest module for tracking nests, eggs, nestlings and nest visits. The app replaces paper forms and allows data to be recorded directly in the field — even without an internet connection. Data is automatically synchronised with the cloud. Catches can be exported to Griel XML format for submission to the Vogeltrekstation.",
